    dc:title "Descriptions of the larva and pupa of Gymnetis pudibunda Burmeister, 1866 (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Cetoniinae: Gymnetini), with notes on natural history and a key to the known larvae of New World Gymnetini" ;
