<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7012274>
    dc:description "Figures 4–7. Gymnetis pudibunda, third instar.(4) Left mandible, in (a) dorsal,(b) lateral,and (c) ventral views; (5) right mandible, in (a) ventral, (b) lateral, and (c) dorsal views; (6) left maxilla, (a) dorsal view, (b) apex of mala showing unci, and (c) stridulatory teeth on maxilla; (7) labium, (a) dorsal view, (b) hypopharyngeal sclerome, and (c) lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7012274/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

